                        <p>
                            <b>Choice of expression of Delivery Location</b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>Choice is per the DeliveryLocationType of the birth location.</b>
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <b>Where the coded value is in the set [0,2,3,4,7], IdentifiedDeliveryLocation shall be used.</b>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <b>Where the coded value is not in this set, DeliveryLocation shall be used.</b>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </text>
