                                <li>The code attribute will contain the appropriate value from the DeliveryLocationType vocabulary</li>
                            </ul>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The codeSystem attribute will contain the OID "2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.17.173"</li>
