                        <text>
                            <p>The identifier of the assigned organisation acting as health care provider.  This will be :</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>GP Practice Code - where the PatientCareProvisionType is "1" (Primary Care)  </li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>The Identifier External datatype flavour is used to carry this information as  follows:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The <em>root</em> attribute will contain an OID with the value  "2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.4.3"  </li>
                                <li>The <em>extension</em> attribute will contain the GP Practice Code </li>
                            </ul>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
